quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,97,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Muntaŵilani chakutaŵa (chiwukuta) ni mumponye m’moto waukali.”"
  37,98,"Basi ŵasachile kuntendela jwalakwe malindi, ni twatesile kuŵa ŵapasi kusyene."
  37,99,"(Ibrahima) ni jwatite: “Chisimu une ngwaula kwa Ambuje ŵangu (Allah), takanjongole.”"
  38,76,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Une ni jwambone nnope kumpunda jwalakweju, mwangumbile une kuumila m’moto, ni mun'gumbile jwalakweju kuumila mwilongo."
  38,77,"(Allah) jwatite: “Basi kopokani mwalakwemo, mwanti chisimu mmwe (sano) n’di ŵakuŵinjidwa.”"
  38,78,"“Soni chisimu pachanya penu pana malweso Gangu mpaka Lisiku Lyamalipilo.”"
  39,61,"Ni tachajokola Allah aŵala ŵaŵaliji ni woga (wakun’jogopa Jwalakwe) ligongo lyakupunda kwao (kwakupata ntendele wa ku Mbepo), yakusakala ngasiyakwaya, nambo soni ŵanganyao ngasaŵa ŵakudandaula."
  39,62,"Allah ni Nkugumba chilichose, soni Jwalakwe pa chindu chilichose juŵele Nkuchengeta."
  39,63,"Gaŵele Gakwe makiyi ga kumawunde ni petaka. Sano aŵala ŵaakaaniile ma Ȃya ga Allah, ŵanganyao niŵali ŵakwasika."
  40,40,"“Jwatapanganye chakusakala chilichose, basi ngaalipidwa ikaŵeje chakulandana mpela chichocho, soni juchapanganye chambone chilichose, kwali taŵe jwannume kapena jwankongwe aku juli tachipedwaga lisiki kwalakweko mwangaŵalanjila.”jwakulupilila, basi ŵanganyao tachijinjila ku Mbepo,"
  40,41,"“Soni E ŵandu ŵangu! Ligongo chichi une ngum’bilanjila jenumanja ku chokoko, sano jenumanja ni nkumilanjila une ku Moto!”"
  40,42,"“Nkumilanjila une kuti nankaane Allah ni nam’bwanganye Jwalakwe ni ichindu yanganingola nayo umanyilisi, kutendaga une ngum’bilanjila ku (Allah) Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwakululuka kusyene!”"
  41,19,"Ni (mwakumbusyani) lisiku lyatachisonganganyisyidwa amagongo ŵa Allah wa ku Moto, basi ni tachiŵa ali nkwalidwa m’mikutula-mikutula."
  41,20,"Kwikanila ndema jatachiuŵichilila (Motowo) gachachonjela mawiwi gao, meso gao, kwisa soni mapende gao pa yaŵaliji nkupanganya."
  41,21,"Ni tachiti ku mapende gao: “Ligongo chichi jenumanja kutuchonjela uwwe?” Galakwe gachiti: “Atuŵechetekasyisye Allah Ajula jwaakuchiŵechetesyaga chindu chilichose, Jwalakwe ni juŵan’gumbile jenumanja kundanda kwene, soni Kukwakwe (sano) nkuuchisyidwa.”"
  42,4,"Iŵele Yakwe (yosope) yaili kumawunde ni yaili petaka, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwapenani kusyene, Jwankulungwa nnope."
  42,5,"Mawunde gakusigalaga panandi kuti gapasuchepasuche pachanya pakwe (ligongo lyakun’jogopa Allah), ni Achimalaika akuluswejesyaga lumbili lwa M’mbuje gwao (Allah), ni kwaŵendelaga chikululuko ŵali petaka. Manyililani yanti chisimu Allah ni Jwali Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope."
  42,6,"Sano aŵala ŵaalitendele (inepe) yangaŵaga Jwalakwe (Allah) kuŵa akwagosa, Allah ni Nkwaasuunga ŵanganyao (pa itendo yao yangalumbana kuti chiŵalipile), soni mmwe nganim'ba nkwachengeta jwao."